        <p>This is the database backend for the buying/selling operations of Athena Books, an
        independently owned e-commerce bookstore that sells approximately 100,000 books per year,
        generating an annual revenue of $2.2 million. The bookstore has one location and ships
        approximately 50,000 orders annually to over 35,000 new and repeat customers across the
        United States. The average price of a book is $22 and the average order is $44. This database
        will track customers’ contact and mailing information, along with the items they have ordered. It
        also tracks the bookstore’s current inventory and price per item, along with authors and
        publishers of the available books</p>
